<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3819] TrueType glyphs not displayed in rendering on Windows 10</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3819</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On windows 10, most glyphs from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1743&quot; title=&quot;OutOfMemoryError in fontbox&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1743&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1743&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; are not displayed, only &quot;test&quot; is shown, for the other lines only squares are shown. The embedded fonts are broken so PDFBox uses the OS fonts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The format type of the postscript table is 3, which means that no postscript information is provided. Apple advises against this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
